      <title>The House passed a budget resolution. What's next? And, a tactic to decrease bird flu</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/26/g-s1-50799/up-first-newsletter-house-budget-passed-elon-musk-doge-bird-flu</link>
