v class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 Caitlin Shetterly                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Caitlin Shetterly                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;In March 2014, newly pregnant Caitlin Shetterly was feeling vulnerable and anxious while on a cross-country flight home. After 9/11, flying made her nervous. When she asked the man sitting next to her if he ever gets nervous, his answer made her body relax. The phrase her unsung hero used &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/25/nx-s1-5302886/unsung-hero-strangers-words-family-mantra-nervous-flying" target="_blank"&gt;became a family touchstone&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fabric giant Joann is &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/25/nx-s1-5307907/joann-closing-stores-bankruptcy" target="_blank"&gt;going out of business&lt;/a&gt; and closing all of its roughly 800 stores across the U.S. after more than 80 years as a major national retailer.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Diana Taurasi, a guard for the Phoenix Mercury, &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/25/g-s1-50737/diana-taurasi-wnba-phoenix-mercury-retires" target="_blank"&gt;has retired&lt;/a&gt;. She leaves her basketball career with three WNBA titles, three NCAA titles and six Olympic gold medals.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/859721331/suzanne-nuyen"target="_blank"   &gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Suzanne Nuyen&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://chrt.fm/track/138C95/prfx.byspotify.com/e/play.podtrac.com/npr-510318/traffic.megaphone.fm/NPR9475959504.mp3?d=847&amp;size=13563238&amp;e=1198908835&amp;t=podcast&amp;p=510318&amp;sc=siteplayer" type="audio/mpeg"/>
      <category>Up First Newsletter</category>
    </item>
