5%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 1200w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/1600/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 1600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/1800/quality/85/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG 1800w" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG" sizes="(min-width: 1300px) 763px, (min-width: 1025px) calc(100vw - 496px), (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 171px), calc(100vw - 30px)" class="img" type="image/jpeg" /&gt;             &lt;img src="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/1100/quality/50/format/jpeg/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG" data-template="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1830x1372+0+0/resize/{width}/quality/{quality}/format/{format}/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F15%2F8a%2Fb4bed40843508a891fd3743c99ad%2Fimg-0012-2.JPG" class="img" alt="NPR&amp;#039;s Adrian Ma remembers his girlfriend, civil rights lawyer Kiah Duggins, who was a passenger on the American Airlines flight that collided with a military helicopter and crashed into the Potomac River." loading="lazy" /&gt;         &lt;/picture&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="credit-caption"&gt;     &lt;div class="caption-wrap"&gt;         &lt;div class="caption" aria-label="Image caption"&gt;             &lt;p&gt;                 NPR's Adrian Ma remembers his girlfriend, civil rights lawyer Kiah Duggins, who was a passenger on the American Airlines flight that collided with a military helicopter and crashed into the Potomac River.                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Adrian Ma                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;p&gt;NPR host Adrian Ma's girlfriend, Kiah Duggins, was on the American Airlines flight that crashed into the Potomac River after colliding with a military helicopter near Ronald Reagan Washington National Airport. No one survived the crash. As the news emerged, Ma was at the airport waiting to pick up Duggins, who had just visited a family member who had recently undergone surgery. Duggins was "like sunshine personified," Ma says. He speaks with NPR about &lt;a href="https://one.npr.org/?sharedMediaId=g-s1-49853:nx-s1-5357223-1" target="_blank"&gt;how that night unfolded&lt;/a&gt; and shared his &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/02/20/g-s1-49853/dc-plane-crash-american-airlines" target="_blank"&gt;memories of his late girlfriend&lt;/a&gt;. "My hope is that I can sort of exorcise the pain that keeps building in my chest," he says. "I think the more that I can plant just a little sense of who this person was in people's minds, the more that she can live on, in a sense."&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;h3 class="edTag"&gt;Weekend picks&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;div id="resg-s1-50077" class="bucketwrap image large"&gt;             &lt;div     class="imagewrap has-source-dimensions"     data-crop-type=""     style="         --source-width: 1198;         --source-height: 674;     " &gt;         &lt;picture&gt;             &lt;source srcset="https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1198x674+1+0/resize/400/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F6c%2F04f8de2546f2b1b3c0046eb92f0b%2Fpchh-paddington-landscape-wide-b20c4475ee2a8ed275a74461067e25813b8a50f2.jpg 400w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1198x674+1+0/resize/600/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F6c%2F04f8de2546f2b1b3c0046eb92f0b%2Fpchh-paddington-landscape-wide-b20c4475ee2a8ed275a74461067e25813b8a50f2.jpg 600w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1198x674+1+0/resize/800/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F6c%2F04f8de2546f2b1b3c0046eb92f0b%2Fpchh-paddington-landscape-wide-b20c4475ee2a8ed275a74461067e25813b8a50f2.jpg 800w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1198x674+1+0/resize/900/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fa7%2F6c%2F04f8de2546f2b1b3c0046eb92f0b%2Fpchh-paddington-landscape-wide-b20c4475ee2a8ed275a74461067e25813b8a50f2.jpg 900w, https://npr.brightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/1198x674+1+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2